<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="accessibility">Accessibility</h2>

<section class="developers-data-flow" id="flow-accessibility-issue">
    <header class="developers-data-flow__header">
        <h3 class="developers-data-flow__title">Accessibility issue</h3>
        <span class="developers-data-flow__kind">Workflow</span>
    </header>
    <partial name="_DataFlowDiagram" model='("a11y", flowAccessibility)' />
    <div class="developers-data-flow__stages">
        <h4 class="developers-data-flow__label">Captured at</h4>
        <div class="developers-data-flow__body">
            <ul>
                <li><code>POST /accessibility/products/{productDocumentId}/issues</code> &mdash; create issue (legacy AdminLTE; will migrate to Modern admin).</li>
                <li><code>POST /accessibility/issues/{id}/comments</code> &mdash; threaded discussion.</li>
                <li><code>POST /accessibility/products/{productDocumentId}/retest-request</code> &mdash; auditor retest request.</li>
                <li><code>POST /accessibility/statements/{id}/verify</code> &mdash; verification request.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h4 class="developers-data-flow__label">Stored in</h4>
        <div class="developers-data-flow__body">
            <ul>
                <li><code>AccessibilityIssue</code> for the headline.</li>
                <li><code>IssueWcagCriterion</code> (one row per WCAG ref).</li>
                <li><code>IssueComment</code> (per-comment) + <code>IssueHistory</code> (per state change).</li>
                <li><code>AccessibilityRetestRequest</code> / <code>StatementVerificationRequest</code> for workflow events.</li>
                <li><code>AuditHistory</code> for the broader audit trail on the product.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h4 class="developers-data-flow__label">Surfaces in</h4>
        <div class="developers-data-flow__body">
            <ul>
                <li>Product detail &mdash; <code>/accessibility/products/{productDocumentId}</code>.</li>
                <li>Issue detail &mdash; <code>/accessibility/issues/{id}</code>.</li>
                <li>Modern operations hub &mdash; <code>/modern/operations/service-register</code> shows the accessibility statement status per product.</li>
                <li>Reporting hub &mdash; <code>/modern/reporting/accessibility</code>.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h4 class="developers-data-flow__label">Triggers</h4>
        <div class="developers-data-flow__body">
            Resolving the last open issue marks the retest request as eligible; verification updates <code>ProductAccessibility.StatementStatus</code> and emails the service owner via <code>AccessibilityEmailConfiguration</code>.
        </div>

        <h4 class="developers-data-flow__label">Downstream</h4>
        <div class="developers-data-flow__body">
            <ul>
                <li>JSON API &mdash; <code>/api/v1/accessibility</code>.</li>
                <li>Published statement page (rendered on the front-end product page).</li>
                <li>PowerBI &mdash; useful as a <code>FactAccessibilityIssue</code> with <code>DimProduct</code> + <code>DimWcag</code>.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

